reviewText: It's not the most professional draping, but aside from that, the techniques are useful in our clinic.
Awful and outdated. The body mechanics are atrocious and so is the draping. The techniques are boring and basic. I'm in school for massage therapy and found these DVDs embarrassing.
Very detailed and interesting,easy to put in practice. Great explanation of the muscles on which you will be working.
We watched these videos when I was in school & loved them. Although I have been a LMT for many years I bought them as a refresher & was not disappointed.
Great purchase, a lot of helpful info.
Sean Riehl has produced a superior DVD set on Deep Tissue bodywork. He clearly knows his profession and is able to relay it in a clear way that is easy to understand and duplicate.
One of the better "Real Bodywork Dvds"!
